•increased revenues associated with agreements executed in connection with Big Spring Gathering System and Delek Trucking acquisitions, which were effective March 31, 2020 and May 1, 2020, respectively; and
•increased revenues at our El Dorado Gathering System and Magnolia Pipeline as result of increased throughput during the year ended December 31, 2020 when compared to the year ended December 31, 2019.
